fields.inlineHelpText: ROI is Net Gain. (Total Amount Won - Actual Cost) / Actual Cost
fields.label: Campaign ROI
fields.name: Campaign_ROI__c

fields.calculatedFormula:
IF(  Campaign_ROI__c  < 1, IMAGE('/resource/1250029193000/dollar_zero', 'zero') ,
IF(Campaign_ROI__c < 1.5, IMAGE('/resource/1250029230000/dollar_one', 'one'),
IF(Campaign_ROI__c < 2.0, IMAGE('/resource/1250029263000/dollar_two', 'two') ,
IF(Campaign_ROI__c < 2.5, IMAGE('/resource/1250029415000/dollar_three', 'three') ,
IF(Campaign_ROI__c < 3, IMAGE('/resource/1250029446000/dollar_four', 'four') ,
IMAGE('/resource/1250029472000/dollar_five', 'five') ) ) ) )
)
